data.description: Sun City offers complete resort-style amenities. Home fully renovated & turn-key; sits on a quiet, corner lot w many upgrades! Eat-in kitchen w Breakfast Bar, New SS Smart Appliances, Quartz Countertops & professionally painted cabinets. New LED lighting & ceiling fans throughout. Cozy Guest room w Smart TV & newly renovated bathroom beside. This layout gives privacy to all. Hidden laundry w new W/D. Great Room has  72in Smart TV to watch Games/Movies. Large cozy Primary w fully renovated bath w walk-in closet. Garage has room for Golf Cart/Tools/Beach supplies. Carolina Room can be an office, place to exercise, or unwind. "Welcome Home!"
